"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Usually, advertising communicates information in three types: audio, visual, and language. It is a more common case that an advertisement is a mixture of the three. In radio advertisements, music is always accompanied by language; on TV and motion pictures, music and language illustration are mixed with each other. In magazines and newspapers, advertisements are a combination of pictures and language of written information. Although music and pictures can provide some hints, or create a kind of atmosphere, the information about the product is limited. Even worse, it may lead to misunderstanding. Thus, we may say that language in a way provides more exact, detailed and dependable information whereas music and pictures only act as a supplementary means in advertising. Advertising language, playing a role of communication and persuasion, has developed its own features.\",\"timestamp\":1638955795,\"title\":\" Usually, advertising communicates\"},\"digest\":\"VPjV5PNei1sswd8VCgmJPphJD8hMFenzdTUEwnBsh2I\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x010572794c3c7a8586a5b3F25acB217c6c35dA96\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Wlf4nRVBll8ALVR0vQG6867UfROYKdJ6H-6kIhGwJuE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"jZucp4mj1_JisoR2qpKbyS2Y5VzD2R_yCYX8GmWQBi0\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"I_26U9qB-1ZMAoiKBEPyc_ZTkWfRbaOYNcgH4bTDmKx0fpoLvY_j9dlbfQsYwMYrRxBLkj0thadcxn5NsS0vrA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xc27078f99798df35b05109917e60fb0e63d37b07bd11d5d4321fc494cb6eeb16598ea551bd98373c9c84806ab54ad3c3c5b07f88e788c633932a0beeef25a3b31c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Wlf4nRVBll8ALVR0vQG6867UfROYKdJ6H-6kIhGwJuE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"jZucp4mj1_JisoR2qpKbyS2Y5VzD2R_yCYX8GmWQBi0\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}}